
'''Inkronu Afahyɛ''' afahyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Sopomu a ɛbɛn Shama wɔ Atɔe  Mantam mu wɔ Ghana no di. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a edikan no mu.<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>

== Afahyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>.

== Mfaso ==
